OL,6,FRaids by immigration officials on
OL,7,Fbusinesses suspected of using illegal
OL,8,Fworkers across south Wales has led to
OL,9,Fmore than 30 arrests.
OL,11,FITV Wales was given exclusive access
OL,12,Fto the operation carried out by Home
OL,13,FOffice Immigration Compliance and
OL,14,FEnforcement officers who targeted a
OL,15,Fnumber of car washes, vape shops and
OL,16,Frestaurants during a week-long
OL,17,Fcrackdown.
