OL,3,CCrackdown on car washes over illegal
OL,4,Cemployment as firms face fines of #60k
OL,6,FDuring this week, across Wales and the
OL,7,Fwest of England, ICE officers raided
OL,8,F50 businesses, making 35 arrests, with
OL,9,F22 civil penalties handed out.
OL,11,FIn the last quarter of last year, more
OL,12,Fthan #200,000 worth of fines were
OL,13,Fhanded out to business owners in Wales
OL,14,Fwho were employing illegal workers.
OL,16,FOfficers told us that car washes, vape
OL,17,Fshops, nail bars and restaurants are
OL,18,Fthe types of businesses where the most
OL,19,Fillegal employment takes place.
