OL,3,CCrackdown on car washes over illegal
OL,4,Cemployment as firms face fines of #60k
OL,6,FBusiness caught employing people with
OL,7,Fno right to work in the UK can faces
OL,8,Ffines up to #60,000.
OL,10,FOne officer told us: "This is
OL,11,Fsomething we're looking to clamp down
OL,12,Fon.
OL,14,F"Particularly in terms of car washes,
OL,15,Fwe've found recently an awful lot of
OL,16,Fillegal employment, a lot of
OL,17,Fexploitation, so that's something
OL,18,Fwe're going to look at.
