OL,3,CCrackdown on car washes over illegal
OL,4,Cemployment as firms face fines of #60k
OL,6,F"We'll look to speak to all of the
OL,7,Fworkers. Part of it is making sure
OL,8,Fthat they're okay, it's not just about
OL,9,Fthe illegal workers, it's about making
OL,10,Fsure they're not being exploited,
OL,11,Fabused in any way.
OL,13,F"We'll do some checks to confirm what
OL,14,Ftheir status is, whether they've got
OL,15,Fpermission to work.
OL,17,F"If they've not got permission to
OL,18,Fwork, then they may well be arrested.
