OL,3,CCrackdown on car washes over illegal
OL,4,Cemployment as firms face fines of #60k
OL,6,F"In terms of the company, if we do
OL,7,Ffind illegal workers there, they can
OL,8,Fbe fined up to #45,000 if it's the
OL,9,Ffirst time, and #60,000 if it's the
OL,10,Fsecond time they've been caught with
OL,11,Fillegal workers."
OL,13,FIllegal employment is damaging to the
OL,14,Fworker, the company and our economy,
OL,15,Fand the message from these immigration
OL,16,Fofficers to companies in Wales
OL,17,Fbreaking the rules is: they will catch
OL,18,Fup with you.
